{
  "texts": [
    "This layer assigned labels to each word then train the network using annotated data and assess the model's performance on test dataset.",
    "Singh et al. [82] proposed an annotated benchmark corpus for Gurmukhi script and also trained a model on the Spacy tool which contains 12k-sentences only using Punjabi corpus data.",
    "The remaining 3k-words were utilized to validate the results using the F1-score, which was picked as the evaluation metric using deep learning [76].",
    "In this study, a unique method for extracting named entities from sentences written in the Gurmukhi script of the Punjabi language is proposed.",
    "This approach classifies named entities into six individual forms."
  ]
}